Programming Project 2 by Saurabh Hindlekar
CPSC 8270
5|o34|<1|\|[, 1|\| |_337

For pizzazz I have added intentional misspelling. 
Some examples 
bai --- bye
ceak --- cake
nd --- and
d00d --- dude
form --- from
guise --- guys

Instructions 
Make and run ./run 
crtl-D to exit. 

Test cases 
Encoder Input: Encode this to leet
Encoder Output: 3|\|<()|)3 7hai5 7() |_337
