Pizzaz test
Encoder Input: Hi guys! It is my birthday today. I come from United States and bring cake from Russia. Bye Dude.
Encoder Output & Decoder Input: |-|1 guise! 17 15 |V|`/ 81|27|-||)4`/ 7()|)4`/. 1 <()|V|3 form \_\|\|173|) 574735 nd 8|21|\|[, ceak form |2\_\5514. 8`/3 |)\_\|)3.
Decoder Output: hi guys! it is my birthday today. i come from united states and bring cake from russia. bye dude.
 

